      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * John Philip Fishburn</b>\n</p><p><b>John Philip Fishburn</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist and electrical engineer from the <a href=\"/Bell_Laboratories\" title=\"Bell Laboratories\">Bell Laboratories</a>. He defended his Ph.D. thesis in 1981 at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Wisconsin-Madison\">University of Wisconsin-Madison</a> on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distributed_algorithm\">distributed algorithms</a> including the <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallelization</a> of <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> under the supervision of <a href=\"/Raphael_Finkel\" title=\"Raphael Finkel\">Raphael Finkel</a>. The routine <i>Calphabeta</i> in his thesis <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is mentioned by <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> as base of a <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a> implementation <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. In his 1983 paper <i>Another optimization of alpha-beta search</i>, John Philip Fishburn introduced <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a> <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1980_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1980 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1980_...\">1980 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1980 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Raphael_Finkel\" title=\"Raphael Finkel\">Raphael Finkel</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i>Parallel Alpha-Beta Search on Arachne.</i> <a href=\"/IEEE\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE</a> International Conference on Parallel Processing, pp. 235-243.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1056450&amp;dl=ACM&amp;coll=DL&amp;CFID=26266656&amp;CFTOKEN=86225814\">An optimization of alpha-beta search</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#SIG\" title=\"ACM\">SIGART Bulletin</a>, No. 72 </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=909940&amp;coll=DL&amp;dl=GUIDE&amp;CFID=26266656&amp;CFTOKEN=86225814\">Analysis of Speedup in Distributed Algorithms</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Wisconsin-Madison\">University of Wisconsin-Madison</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.wisc.edu/techreports/1981/TR431.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i>Some Optimizations of Alpha-Beta Search.</i> Computer Science Department, University of Wisconsin-Madison. Appendix to Ph.D. thesis</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i>Three Optimizations of Alpha-Beta Search</i>. Computer Science Department, University of Wisconsin-Madison. Appendix to Ph.D. thesis</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Raphael_Finkel\" title=\"Raphael Finkel\">Raphael Finkel</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1982</b>). <i>Parallelism in Alpha-Beta Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_%28journal%29\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 19, No. 1 </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1056623.1056628&amp;coll=DL&amp;dl=GUIDE&amp;CFID=26266656&amp;CFTOKEN=86225814\">Another optimization of alpha-beta search</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#SIG\" title=\"ACM\">SIGART Bulletin</a>, No. 84, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B2pvWWlf39g-cjJpZkc1cDhfbkk/view\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Raphael_Finkel\" title=\"Raphael Finkel\">Raphael Finkel</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i>Improved Speedup Bounds for Parallel Alpha-Beta Search</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TPAMI\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence</a>, Vol. 5, No. 1</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John P. Fishburn</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/A-Depth-Decreasing-Heuristic-for-Combinational-Or-a-Fishburn/3fc16ca5e4588a5150391305a43cdc914b3d206d\">A Depth-Decreasing Heuristic for Combinational Logic: Or How To Convert a Ripple-Carry Adder Into A Carry-Lookahead Adder Or Anything in-between</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/dac/dac90.html\">DAC 1990</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John P. Fishburn</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i>Clock Skew Optimization</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOC\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computers</a>, Vol. 39</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ece.umn.edu/~sachin/grad/grad.html\">Harsha Sathyamurthy</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ece.umn.edu/~sachin/index.html\">Sachin S. Sapatnekar</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John P. Fishburn</a> (<b>1995</b>) <i>Speeding up Pipelined Circuits through a Combination of Gate Sizing and Clock Skew Optimization</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/iccad/iccad1995.html\">ICCAD 1995</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John P. Fishburn</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/780126/\">Optimization-based calibration of a static timing analyzer to path delay measurements</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/iscas/iscas1999-6.html\">ISCAS 1999</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John P. Fishburn</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0020019001002678\">Solving a system of difference constraints with variables restricted to a finite set</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Processing_Letters\">Information Processing Letters</a>, Vol. 82, No. 3</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John P. Fishburn</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i>Search-Based Opening Book Construction</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B2pvWWlf39g-NWN0OUpkRE0tem8/view\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B2pvWWlf39g-Z2ZmbHhtWTUwZFE/view\">2017 edition</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Search-based opening book construction</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 1</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=661996\">Computer Chess Strength</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  February 28, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=662580\">How much benefit from opening book?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 06, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=663148\">reversed-color transpositions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 11, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Color_Flipping\" title=\"Color Flipping\">Color Flipping</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=674910\">move frequency in chessbase</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 10, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/ChessBase_(Database)\" title=\"ChessBase (Database)\">ChessBase (Database)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=698871\">Search-Based Opening Book Construction</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2016 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63862\">Search-Based Opening Book Construction</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 29, 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=82417\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - John Fishburn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Philip_Fishburn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i>Analysis of Speedup in Distributed Algorithms</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Wisconsin-Madison\">University of Wisconsin-Madison</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.wisc.edu/techreports/1981/TR431.pdf\">pdf</a>, <i>Calphabeta</i> at page 167</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i>Relative Efficiency of Alpha-beta Implementations</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI1983\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 1983</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~tony/OldPapers/IJCAI-83.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Philip Fishburn</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1056623.1056628&amp;coll=DL&amp;dl=GUIDE&amp;CFID=26266656&amp;CFTOKEN=86225814\">Another optimization of alpha-beta search</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#SIG\" title=\"ACM\">SIGART Bulletin</a>, No. 84,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B2pvWWlf39g-cjJpZkc1cDhfbkk/view\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Jean-Christophe_Weill\" title=\"Jean-Christophe Weill\">Jean-Christophe Weill</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>Experiments With the NegaC* Search - An Alternative for Othello Endgame Search.</i> <a href=\"/2nd_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"2nd Computer Olympiad\">Heuristic Programming in AI 2</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/f/Fishburn:John_P=.html\">dblp: John P. Fishburn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=698871\">Search-Based Opening Book Construction</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63862\">Search-Based Opening Book Construction</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Fishburn</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 29, 2017</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301005717\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 133/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 278/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:3349-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301005717 and revision id 4586\n -->\n"
